{"tid":2476513,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[4月此元和津也] ODD TAXI","createTime":"2021-04-05T14:24:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T19:30:34.000Z","uid":4618,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a7e2070239f69ac7c454946f5ff383c2fcf17ba3","tid":2476513,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T14:24:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmW48WH974vgN5K5pHasRcKK251kaebHocHLXww6qb9tn9?filename=2NOEHxb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2NOEHxb.jpg&h=e95db5a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNpBA73mXKXVYceY3MTrUV4Ti2nnMp3NH8Z9yUi57vHLE?filename=c0g66YR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc0g66YR.jpg&h=92710634&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《ODD TAXI》（日語：オッドタクシー）是由P.I.C.S.和OLM製作的一部原創動畫。<br />\n<br />\n故事簡介：<br />\n<br />\n平凡的出租車司機・小戶川。<br />\n沒有親戚，也不想與人扯上關係，有點古怪且寡言的司機。<br />\n興趣是在睡前聽落語以及工作時聽收音機。<br />\n目前，唯一有聯絡的是醫生朋友・剛力以及高中同級生・柿花。<br />\n<br />\n本該載着各式各樣的乘客，平凡的每一日，<br />\n小戶川與一名失蹤的女孩事件扯上了關係&hellip;。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPV<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rS228HesD9g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FrS228HesD9g&d=Ai36%2FzMZEIUB39LyUGzRLW7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=d4789fa2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rS228HesD9g</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zyRA29X85YI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzyRA29X85YI&d=Ai36%2FzMZEIUB39LyUGzRLW7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=816ae6cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zyRA29X85YI</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4sFbCZOHHfc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4sFbCZOHHfc&d=Ai36%2FzMZEIUB39LyUGzRLW7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=a32c4ee6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4sFbCZOHHfc</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>STAFF</strong><br />\n企  劃・原作：P.I.C.S.<br />\n劇  本：此元和津也（P.I.C.S. management）<br />\n監  督：木下麦（P.I.C.S.）<br />\n副監督 ：新田典生<br 